extends ../base
include ../mixins/video

block content
   .profile__data 
      if !loggedInUser.avatarUrl
         div.avatar(style="background:gray")
      else
         img(src="/" + user.avatarUrl).avatar
      h3=user.name
   .video-grid 
      each video in user.videos 
         +video(video)
      else 
         span.empty__message 업로드한 비디오가 없습니다.

